Definition: a mechanical device consisting of a cylindrical tube around which the hair is wound to curl it
Example: a woman with her head full of curlers is not a pretty sight
Synonyms: verb, contact, curl, hair_curler, roller, roll, crimper, mechanical_device, a, mechanical, device, consisting, of, cylindrical, tube, around, which, the, hair, is, wound, to, it, woman, with, her, head, full, curlers, not, pretty, sight
Category: noun.artifact
